content:
As your sales reps use Sales Cloud Everywhere, they can choose the fields they want to see and arrange them the way they want to work.

This change applies to Lightning Experience in Starter, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer editions. It is available beginning April 18, 2024.

In Sales Cloud Everywhere, go to an opportunity, contact, account, or lead page. Select a record to go to the detail page. In the Key Fields section, click the edit gear. Add any available fields to the key fields section and remove the fields that arenâ€™t important to you. Update the order of the fields, if needed, and save your choices.

Enable and Disable the Salesforce Everywhere Chrome Extension.
title: Customize Your Sales Cloud Experience
